We use Node.js 11.x LTS since a while and were wondering if Titanium SDK 8 will officially support it. Right now, it seems not officially supported, although everything works really good! Warning:
{code}
[WARN]  Support for Node.js v11.6.0 has not been verified for Titanium SDK 8.0.0
[WARN]  If you run into issues, try downgrading to Node.js v10
{code}
